snippet.title: Starwave - Official Release Date Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Watch the trailer for Starwave for a look at this vibrant VR rhythm game coming to Meta Quest 2 and Meta Quest 3 on September 5, 2024. Starwave launches you into a cosmic voyage of high-energy music and exhilarating freeform movement inviting you to discover a new way to flow. Feel the rhythm of the universe as you soar through distant galaxies bringing color and light to the night sky.
